These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, malaysian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, golf
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, tram
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the malaysian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | malaysian    | dutch |
| Sport         | golf | skateboarding    |
| Transport     | bus     | tram      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, fanta
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, pakistani
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the colombian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | fanta  | milk   |
| Nationality   | pakistani | colombian  |
| Transport     | trike   | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, hiking
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, romance
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, rowing
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4
2. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | gardening   | hiking  |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | action  |
| Sport         | weightlifting   | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
