The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, action
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, airplane
1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
2. the person eating corn is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | corn | peas |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | spy   |
| Transport     | airplane       | taxi      |

