.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: papaya, cherry
The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, designer
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the security-guard##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
3. the person eating papaya is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | cherry | papaya     |
| Job     | designer | security-guard |
| Sport   | tennis | cycling    |

