.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, chess
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, japanese
2 different pets are kept: turtle, fish
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the brazilian is on the left of the japanese##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | chess | card-games |
| Nationality   | brazilian     | japanese     |
| Pet           | fish          | turtle     |

