The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, airplane
1. the person watching spy movies is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of soul is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | musical |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | soul  |
| Transport     | airplane | bus    |

 